
# Personal Portfolio

A modern and responsive personal portfolio website built using HTML and CSS.

## Features

- Responsive Design
- Clean and Modern UI
- Sidebar Navigation
- Profile Section
- Contact Information
- Social Media Links

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3

## Project Structure

```
PORTFOLIO/
├── index.html
├── css/
│   └── style.css
├── images/
│   └── Shahbaz.png
└── README.md
```

## How to Run

1. Download or clone this repository.
2. Open the project folder.
3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

